	<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak direction-ltr">
	<div class="govspeak">
	<p>This is a list of documents and policies maintained schools need to have in place to meet their statutory responsibilities. Each item listed is linked to supporting guidance or tools to help you to meet your legal obligations.</p>
	
	<h2 id="staff">Staff</h2>
	
	<ul>
	<li>
	<p><a rel="external" href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/teacher-appraisal-and-capability-model-policy">Teacher appraisal and capability model policy</a></p>

	</li>
	<li>
	<p><a rel="external" href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/school-teachers-pay-and-conditions">Teacher pay</a></p>

	</li>
	<li>
	<p><a rel="external" href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/staffing-and-employment-advice-for-schools">Staffing and employment advice for schools</a></p>

	</li>
	<li>
	<p><a rel="external" href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/disqualification-under-the-childcare-act-2006">Disqualification under the childcare act 2006</a></p>

	</li>
	</ul>
	
	<h2 id="admission-arrangements">Admission arrangements</h2>
	
	<ul>
	<li>
	<p><a rel="external" href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/school-admissions-code--2">School admissions code</a></p>

	</li>
	<li>
	<p><a rel="external" href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/school-admissions-appeals-code">School admissions appeal code</a></p>

	</li>
	<li>
	<p><a rel="external" href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/summer-born-children-school-admission">Summer-born children school admission</a></p>

	</li>
	<li>
	<p><a rel="external" href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/fair-access-protocols-in-school-admissions">Fair access protocols in school admissions</a></p>

	</li>
	</ul>
	
	<h2 id="school">School</h2>
	
	<ul>
	<li>
	<p><a rel="external" href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/charging-for-school-activities">Charging for school activities</a></p>

	</li>
	<li>
	<p><a rel="external" href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/school-complaints-procedures">School complaints procedures</a></p>

	</li>
	<li>
	<p><a rel="external" href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/data-protection-and-privacy-privacy-notices">Data protection and privacy notices</a></p>

	</li>
	<li>
	<p><a rel="external" href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/data-protection-toolkit-for-schools">Data protection toolkit for schools</a></p>

	</li>
	<li>
	<p><a rel="external" href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/health-and-safety-advice-for-schools">Health and safety advice for schools</a></p>

	</li>
	<li>
	<p><a rel="external" href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/standards-for-school-premises">Standards for school premises</a></p>

	</li>
	<li>
	<p><a rel="external" href="https://www.gov.uk/guidance/good-estate-management-for-schools/the-fundamentals-of-good-estate-management">The fundamentals of good estate management</a></p>
	</li>
	<li>
	<p><a rel="external" href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/school-attendance">School attendance</a></p>

	</li>
	<li>
	<p><a rel="external" href="https://www.gov.uk/guidance/what-maintained-schools-must-publish-online">What maintained schools must publish online</a></p>

	</li>
	<li><p><a rel="external" href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/first-aid-in-schools">First aid in schools</a></p></li>
<li><p><a rel="external" href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/protection-of-biometric-information-of-children-in-schools">Protecting children’s biometric information</a></p></li>
<li><p><a rel="external" href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/driving-school-minibuses-advice-for-schools-and-local-authorities">Driving school mini buses</a></p></li>
	</ul>
	
	<h2 id="pupils">Pupils</h2>
	
	<ul>
	<li>
	<p><a rel="external" href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/keeping-children-safe-in-education--2">Keeping children safe in education</a></p>

	</li>
	<li>
	<p><a rel="external" href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/behaviour-and-discipline-in-schools-guidance-for-governing-bodies">Behaviour and discipline in schools: guidance for governing bodies</a></p>
	</li>
	<li>
	<p><a rel="external" href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/school-exclusion">School exclusion</a></p>

	</li>
	<li>
	<p><a rel="external" href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/sex-and-relationship-education">Sex and relationship education</a></p>

	</li>
	<li>
	<p><a rel="external" href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/send-code-of-practice-0-to-25">Special educational needs and disability code of practice: 0 to 25 years</a></p>
	</li>
	<li>
	<p><a rel="external" href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/supporting-pupils-at-school-with-medical-conditions--3">Supporting pupils at school with medical conditions</a></p>
	</li>
	</ul>
	
	<h2 id="governance">Governance</h2>
	
	<ul>
	<li>
	<p><a rel="external" href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/constitution-of-governing-bodies-of-maintained-schools">Constitution of governing bodies of maintained schools</a></p>
	</li>
	<li>
	<p><a rel="external" href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/governance-handbook">Governance handbook</a></p>

	</li>
	<li><p><a rel="external" href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/working-together-to-safeguard-children--2">Working together to safe guard children</a></p></li>
	</ul>
	
	<p>This information outlines the statutory guidance and policies for maintained schools, you can find the relevant policies for your school type at <a href="admin/publications/867957">statutory policies for schools</a>.</p>

	</div>
